<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Laptop CMS</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
      }
      
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      
      .header {
        background-color: #2563eb;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      
      .content h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #1e3a8a;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      
      .credentials-box {
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      
      .credentials-box p {
        margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      }
      
      .credentials-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      
      .credentials-box strong {
        color: #1e3a8a;
      }
      
      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 35px 0;
      }
      
      .button {
        background-color: #2563eb;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      
      .footer {
        background-color: #f1f5f9;
        padding: 25px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      
      .address {
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #64748b;
      }
      
      .copyright {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Laptop CMS</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to Laptop CMS, <%= name %>!</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for joining us. Your account has been successfully created. Here are your login credentials:</p>
        
        <div class="credentials-box">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
          <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= password %></p>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> <%= role %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>For security reasons, please log in and change your password as soon as possible.</p>
        
        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="https://laptops-cms.example.com/login" class="button">Log In Now</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="address">
          Laptop CMS, Inc.<br>
          38 Savage Square, Kissy<br>
          Freetown, SL
        </p>
        
        <p class="copyright">
          &copy; 2025 Laptop CMS. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>